Saudi Soldier Killed in Exchange of Fire Near Yemeni Borders

-- B y   M o u r a d   H a r o u t u n i a n
-- 
2011-04-12T15:52:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-12/saudi-soldier-killed-in-exchange-of-fire-near-yemeni-borders.html
A Saudi border guard was killed
this morning during an exchange of fire with people trying to
infiltrate into the southern province of Asir on the border with
Yemen, the  Saudi Press Agency  reported, citing the Ministry of
Interior.  During the clash, which took place in the Bateeh area,
patrols arrested an infiltrator while the rest fled to the
mountains, the SPA said, citing Border Guards Spokesman Colonel
Salim Al Silmi.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mourad Haroutunian in Riyadh at 
